| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2142 — Recovery Inhibition (worldleaks)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 74a79466-ad08-5c7c-8b89-6bc837c557b4"
